RedirectMatch 301 ^/about/ https://v2.rivet.iu.edu/about/
RedirectMatch 301 ^/content-guide/ https://brand.iu.edu/
RedirectMatch 301 ^/components/information/changelog/ https://v2.rivet.iu.edu/docs/getting-started/changelog/
RedirectMatch 301 ^/getting-started/ https://v2.rivet.iu.edu/docs/getting-started/